# Local Claude Code tool permission cache -- not app config, and its
# recorded permission entries can capture real command strings (a real
# credential leaked into this exact file once, see docs/DECISIONS.md's
# "Public release" section, C7 2026-07-17). *.local above doesn't catch
# it since the file ends in .json, not .local.
